      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00284"/><hi rend="latintype">Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb168934" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Frankgasse</hi> 1</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00283"/>lieber Arthur</salute></opener><p>an der <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00862-1"/>Ca<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>a<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00862-1">Am Abend fand die <rs type="event" ref="#pmb35382">Uraufführung von <rs ref="#pmb30219" type="work">Das Vermächtnis</rs></rs> statt. <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1898-11-30" subtype="Cf"/>.</note> beko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en
               die Leute die Auskunft, da<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s die Sitze und Logen durch Sie direct zu beziehen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind,
               al<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o was<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>oll machen!</p><closer><signed>Hugo</signed></closer><postscript><p>Es handelt<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich um die Loge »<rs ref="#pmb34331" type="person">Franken<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tein</rs>.«</p></postscript></div>
      </body>
